data.value: 1.This Demo is for the frequency response fuction. 2.We offer 3 kinds of output signal : WhiteNoise , StepSine and Chirp. 3.PXI9527 AO0 will generate the original signal. AI0 is connected direct to AO0. There is a RC circult between AO0 and AI1. The parameters of the RC circult are on the left. 4.Simulation mode is offered. 5.Harmonic Distortion is only offered for StepSine.
